<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>旅游智能规划助手 - TRAE AI 创造力大赛</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <script>
    window._AMapSecurityConfig = {
        securityJsCode: 'aa0fc35d2249d55c8c78f307b71195ac',
    }
</script>
<script src="https://webapi.amap.com/maps?v=2.0&key=b87e57c19df3b4cc00903af692340e21&plugin=AMap.AutoComplete,AMap.Driving,AMap.Transfer,AMap.Geocoder,AMap.Scale,AMap.ToolBar"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="app-container">
        <header class="app-header">
            <h1>🗺️ 旅游智能规划助手</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">智能规划您的完美旅程</p>
        </header>
        <main class="main-content">
            <section class="input-section">
                <div class="card">
                    <h2>📝 规划您的旅行</h2>
                    <form id="travelForm">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>出发城市</label>
                            <div class="city-selector" id="departureSelector">
                                <div class="city-selector-input" id="departureInput" tabindex="0">
                                    <span class="city-placeholder">搜索任意地点...</span>
                                    <svg class="city-arrow" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M2 4l4 4 4-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                                </div>
                                <input type="hidden" id="departureCity" required>
                                <input type="hidden" id="departureLng">
                                <input type="hidden" id="departureLat">
                                <div class="city-dropdown" id="departureDropdown">
                                    <div class="city-search-box">
                                        <svg class="search-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"/></svg>
                                        <input type="text" class="city-search-input" placeholder="输入地点名称，如：丽江古城、乌镇、故宫..." id="departureSearch">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="city-search-results" id="departureSearchResults"></div>
                                    <div class="city-panel">
                                        <div class="city-section">
                                            <div class="city-section-title">🔥 热门出发地</div>
                                            <div class="city-grid" id="departureHotCities"></div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>目的地</label>
                            <div class="city-selector" id="destinationSelector">
                                <div class="city-selector-input" id="destinationInput" tabindex="0">
                                    <span class="city-placeholder">搜索任意地点...</span>
                                    <svg class="city-arrow" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M2 4l4 4 4-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                                </div>
                                <input type="hidden" id="destinationCity" required>
                                <input type="hidden" id="destinationLng">
                                <input type="hidden" id="destinationLat">
                                <div class="city-dropdown" id="destinationDropdown">
                                    <div class="city-search-box">
                                        <svg class="search-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"/></svg>
                                        <input type="text" class="city-search-input" placeholder="输入地点名称，如：丽江古城、乌镇、故宫..." id="destinationSearch">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="city-search-results" id="destinationSearchResults"></div>
                                    <div class="city-panel">
                                        <div class="city-section">
                                            <div class="city-section-title">🔥 热门目的地</div>
                                            <div class="city-grid" id="destinationHotCities"></div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="travelDate">出发日期</label>
                            <input type="date" id="travelDate" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="travelDays">旅行天数</label>
                            <input type="number" id="travelDays" min="1" max="30" value="3" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="budget">总预算 (元)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="budget" min="500" max="100000" value="5000" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>旅行偏好</label>
                            <div class="preference-options">
                                <label class="checkbox-label"><input type="checkbox" name="preference" value="nature" checked><span>🌲 自然风光</span></label>
                                <label class="checkbox-label"><input type="checkbox" name="preference" value="history"><span>🏛️ 历史人文</span></label>
                                <label class="checkbox-label"><input type="checkbox" name="preference" value="food"><span>🍜 美食探店</span></label>
                                <label class="checkbox-label"><input type="checkbox" name="preference" value="instagram"><span>📸 网红打卡</span></label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">开始规划 ✨</button>
                    </form>

                    <!-- 历史记录 -->
                    <section class="history-section" id="historySection" style="display:none;">
                        <div class="history-header">
                            <h4>&#128203; 历史规划</h4>
                            <button type="button" class="history-clear-btn" onclick="clearHistory()">清空</button>
                        </div>
                        <div id="historyList"></div>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="result-section" id="resultSection">
                <!-- 地图选点 -->
                <div class="result-card" id="mapPickerCard">
                    <h3>📍 地图选点</h3>
                    <p class="map-picker-tip">点击地图选择出发地或目的地，也可拖拽标记点调整位置</p>
                    <div id="mapPicker" style="width:100%;height:400px;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="welcome-tip" id="welcomeTip">
                    <div class="tip-icon">🎯</div>
                    <h3>欢迎使用旅游规划助手</h3>
                    <p>请在左侧填写您的旅行信息，点击"开始规划"获取专属旅行方案</p>
                </div>
                <div class="result-card" id="weatherSection" style="display: none;">

                    <h3>🌤️ 目的地天气</h3>

                    <div class="weather-content" id="weatherContent"></div>

                </div>

                <div class="result-card" id="transportSection" style="display: none;">
    <h3>🚄 交通建议</h3>
    <div class="transport-tabs">
        <div class="transport-tab active" data-sort="recommend">推荐</div>
        <div class="transport-tab" data-sort="fastest">最快</div>
        <div class="transport-tab" data-sort="cheapest">最省钱</div>
    </div>
    <div class="transport-summary" id="transportSummary"></div>
    <div class="transport-options" id="transportOptions"></div>
</div>
                <div class="result-card" id="budgetSection" style="display: none;"><h3>💰 预算分配</h3><div class="budget-content"><div class="pie-chart-container"><canvas id="budgetPieChart"></canvas></div><div class="budget-legend" id="budgetLegend"></div></div><div class="budget-details" id="budgetDetails"></div></div>
                <div class="result-card" id="attractionsSection" style="display: none;"><h3>🏞️ 景点推荐</h3><div class="attractions-list" id="attractionsList"></div></div>
                <div class="result-card" id="foodSection" style="display: none;">
                    <h3>🍜 美食推荐</h3>
                    <div class="food-list" id="foodList"></div>
                    <div class="restaurant-section" id="restaurantSection">
                        <h4 class="restaurant-title">🍽\ufe0f 推荐餐厅</h4>
                        <div class="restaurant-list" id="restaurantList"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="result-card" id="hotelSection" style="display: none;">
                    <h3>🏨 住宿推荐</h3>
                    <div id="hotelContent"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="result-card" id="itinerarySection" style="display: none;"><h3>📅 行程规划</h3><div class="itinerary-list" id="itineraryList"></div></div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <footer class="app-footer"><p>由 TRAE AI 驱动的智能旅游规划助手 | 生活娱乐赛道</p></footer>
    </div>

    <script src="app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>